%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22I've%20perfected%20my%20chocolate%20chip%20cookie%20over%20the%20years%2C%20always%20working%20from%20memory.%20To%20my%20sons%2C%20they%20are%20so%20much%20more%20than%20a%20dessert.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Composite%20image.%20On%20the%20left%2C%20the%20author's%20older%20son%20is%20blowing%20out%20a%20giant%20cookie%20cake%20with%20a%20cat%20decoration%20and%20two%20candles%20that%20say%20%26quot%3B11%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20on%20the%20right%2C%20a%20close-up%20of%20chocolate%20chip%20cookies.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4684c065e65d39ff1c8fa5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20sons%20love%20her%20chocolate%20chip%20cookies%20so%20much%20that%20her%20older%20son%20asked%20for%20a%20giant%20chocolate%20chip%20cookie%20instead%20of%20a%20cake%20for%20his%2011th%20birthday.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Kristina%20Wright%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20make%20chocolate%20chip%20cookies%20from%20a%20recipe%20I've%20been%20tweaking%20for%20over%2025%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20sons%20say%20they're%20the%20best%20cookies%20ever%2C%20and%20have%20been%20asking%20me%20to%20write%20down%20the%20'real'%20recipe.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20cookies%20are%20the%20taste%20of%20their%20childhood%2C%20and%20I%20understand%20why%20they're%20so%20connected%20to%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadult-sons-moved-back-in-expenses-increase-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo%20teenage%20sons%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20make%20the%20best%20chocolate%20chip%20cookies%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20accept%20this%20compliment%20with%20the%20appropriate%20amount%20of%20gratitude%20and%20skepticism%2C%20because%20%26quot%3Bmy%26quot%3B%20recipe%20started%20life%20as%20a%20clipping%20from%20a%20women's%20magazine%20at%20least%2025%20years%20ago%2C%20which%20I%20then%20taped%20inside%20my%20%3Cem%3EBetter%20Homes%20and%20Gardens%3C%2Fem%3E%20cookbook%20so%20I%20wouldn't%20lose%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20I've%20changed%20enough%20things%20%E2%80%94%20bread%20flour%20in%20place%20of%20all-purpose%20flour%2C%20half%20the%20amount%20of%20salt%2C%20a%20little%20extra%20vanilla%2C%20no%20nuts%2C%20double%20the%20chocolate%20chips%2C%20chilling%20the%20dough%20when%20the%20kitchen%20is%20hot%20%E2%80%94%20that%20it%20only%20vaguely%20resembles%20the%20original.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20is%20that%20I%20have%20never%20written%20any%20of%20this%20down.%20I%20use%20the%20original%20recipe%20as%20a%20guide%20and%20make%20the%20adjustments%20according%20to%20memory.%20So%20if%20my%20kids%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-famous-chef-has-the-best-chocolate-chip-cookie-recipe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emake%20cookies%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20the%20recipe%20taped%20in%20the%20cookbook%2C%20they'd%20end%20up%20with%20an%20entirely%20different%20cookie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224c2e9e58-b320-41ee-a28a-26d71c65fe5d%5C%22%3EMy%20go-to%20cookie%20recipe%20became%20the%20only%20cookies%20they%20want%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMama%2C%20you%20need%20to%20write%20down%20the%20%3Cem%3Ereal%3C%2Fem%3E%20recipe%2C%26quot%3B%20my%20youngest%20son%20said%2C%20again%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20ago%2C%20when%20I%20was%20baking%20a%20double%20batch%20for%20the%20student%20council%20bake%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20funny%20is%20that%20these%20cookies%20have%20always%20felt%20to%20me%20like%20the%20laziest%2C%20most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-brand-chocolate-chip-cookie-should-i-buy-comparison%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebasic%20cookies%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20world.%20There's%20nothing%20fancy%20about%20them%3B%20I%20don't%20even%20buy%20an%20expensive%20brand%20of%20chocolate%20chips.%20But%20they're%20reliable%20and%20quick%2C%20and%20yes%2C%20delicious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20reason%20they%20became%20such%20a%20fixture%20in%20our%20family%20is%20because%20they%20were%20easy.%20I'd%20always%20enjoyed%20baking%20and%2C%20before%20kids%2C%20would%20regularly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-one-bowl-chocolate-cake-recipe-photos-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebake%20for%20friends%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20coworkers.%20Then%20I%20became%20a%20mother%20in%20my%2040s%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20create%20the%20kind%20of%20home%20where%20homemade%20cookies%20occasionally%20appeared%20after%20hard%20days%2C%20before%20big%20tests%2C%20or%20because%20it%20was%20raining%20outside%20and%20we%20had%20nowhere%20else%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESomewhere%20along%20the%20way%2C%20these%20cookies%20became%20part%20of%20our%20family%20life%20in%20a%20way%20I%20didn't%20plan%20for.%20I%20packed%20them%20into%20school%20lunches%2C%20made%20them%20for%20road%20trips%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-tropical-islands-to-visit-from-frequent-traveler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeach%20vacations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sick%20days%2C%20and%20on%20request.%20When%20someone%20would%20ask%2C%20%26quot%3BCan%20you%20bake%20cookies%3F%26quot%3B%20these%20were%20the%20cookies%20they%20meant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20year%2C%20my%20older%20son%20requested%20a%20giant%20chocolate%20chip%20cookie%20for%20his%20birthday%20instead%20of%20a%20cake.%20I%20told%20him%20I%20could%20order%20one%20from%20the%20grocery%20store%20bakery%2C%20but%20he%20wanted%20me%20to%20use%20my%20recipe.%20So%20that's%20what%20I%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222447%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20son%20smiling%20next%20to%20chocolate%20chip%20cookies%20wrapped%20up%20for%20a%20bake%20sale.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a46853165e65d39ff1c8fad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222447%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20has%20also%20made%20her%20chocolate%20chip%20cookies%20for%20bake%20sales.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Kristina%20Wright%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22271ce253-c783-43c4-9ec4-a036660c28d8%5C%22%3EMy%20kids%20associate%20home%20with%20the%20smell%20of%20my%20cookies%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20once%20in%20a%20while%2C%20one%20of%20my%20sons%20will%20come%20home%20after%20trying%20an%20expensive%20bakery%20cookie%20or%20a%20friend's%20mom's%20cookies%20and%20announce%2C%20with%20complete%20sincerity%2C%20that%20it%20wasn't%20as%20good%20as%20mine.%20This%20makes%20me%20laugh%20every%20single%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20obviously%20better%20cookies%20in%20the%20world%20than%20the%20ones%20I%20make%20in%20my%20kitchen%20with%20grocery%20store%20chocolate%20chips%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20really%20the%20comparison%20they're%20making.%20They%20aren't%20looking%20for%20the%20objectively%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-for-making-best-cookies-from-professional-baker-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20cookie%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20they're%20looking%20for%20the%20taste%20of%20their%20own%20childhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20older%20mom%20and%20a%20writer%2C%20I%20think%20about%20memory%20more%20than%20I%20used%20to.%20I%20think%20about%20what%20my%20children%20will%20remember%20when%20they%20leave%20home%2C%20and%20eventually%20what%20they'll%20remember%20when%20I'm%20gone.%20I've%20spent%20years%20preserving%20the%20pieces%20of%20my%20children's%20lives%20that%20seem%20important.%20I've%20saved%20photographs%20and%20school%20papers%2C%20written%20letters%20and%20blog%20posts%2C%20kept%20journals%20and%20datebooks%20full%20of%20ordinary%20details%20of%20our%20family%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realize%20now%20that%20sometimes%20what%20lasts%20are%20the%20things%20that%20show%20up%20over%20and%20over%20again.%20The%20inside%20jokes%2C%20the%20favorite%20dinners%2C%20the%20holiday%20traditions%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20cookie%20recipe%20made%20so%20many%20times%20that%20its%20smell%20alone%20can%20take%20you%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b34ee0fa-35a8-43cb-addb-1300e5212287%5C%22%3EThe%20cookies%20are%20a%20part%20of%20our%20family%20story%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20day%2C%20my%20boys%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fempty-nester-found-unqiue-way-connect-sons-college-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebe%20in%20college%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20live%20in%20apartments%20and%20homes%20of%20their%20own%2C%20and%20I%20won't%20always%20be%20there%20when%20life%20gets%20hard%20or%20lonely%20or%20overwhelming.%20But%20I%20can%20put%20cookies%20in%20a%20box%20and%20send%20them%20wherever%20they%20are.%20And%2C%20if%20they%20want%20to%2C%20they%20can%20make%20the%20cookies%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20yes%2C%20I'm%20finally%20going%20to%20write%20the%20recipe%20down%2C%20and%20I'll%20make%20each%20of%20them%20a%20copy.%20Maybe%20they'll%20pull%20it%20out%20in%20a%20dorm%20kitchen%20someday.%20Maybe%20they'll%20make%20them%20for%20roommates%2C%20partners%2C%20or%20their%20own%20children.%20Maybe%20one%20day%20they'll%20have%20changed%20the%20recipe%20so%20much%20that%20it%20barely%20resembles%20mine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20I'd%20like%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-chocolate-chip-cookie-recipe-sons-childhood-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783250461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4684c065e65d39ff1c8fa5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-chocolate-chip-cookie-recipe-sons-childhood-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20make%20my%20chocolate%20chip%20cookie%20recipe%20from%20memory.%20My%20sons%20want%20me%2