e%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%2011-year-old%20son%20just%20finished%20fifth%20grade%2C%20and%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20he%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20ADHD%2C%20dyslexia%2C%20and%20dysgraphia.%20He%20has%20trouble%20remembering%20the%20order%20of%20things%20and%20organizing%20his%20thoughts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20him%20a%20new%20computer%20for%20Christmas%2C%20which%20he%20can%20use%20to%20access%20Copilot.%20The%20first%20time%20we%20used%20AI%20together%20was%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteenager-uses-ai-homework-mom-helped-school-write-ai-policy-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehelp%20research%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20school%20essay%20on%20hurricanes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20of%20us%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgithub-copilot-token-uage-pricing-change-reaction-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eworking%20with%20Copilot%3C%2Fa%3E%20open%20on%20the%20side%20of%20his%20essay%20notes.%20Being%20able%20to%20go%20back%20and%20forth%20with%20the%20AI%20and%20ask%20it%20questions%20was%20eye-opening%20for%20him.%20He%20was%20able%20to%20get%20much%20more%20context%20from%20the%20research%20he%20was%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20a%20few%20weeks%20later%2C%20one%20night%2C%20I%20came%20up%20behind%20him%20while%20he%20was%20working%20on%20his%20computer.%20Until%20I%20started%20asking%20questions%2C%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20he%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffintech-company-slash-employee-burned-through-thousands-in-tokens-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20his%20own%20video%20game%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20for%20him%2C%20the%20simplicity%20of%20using%20AI%20is%20what%20he%20loves.%20He%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20a%20coder%20to%20be%20creative%20in%20this%20way.%20This%20is%20a%20perfect%20example%20of%20AI%20not%20taking%20away%20from%20humanity%20or%20creativity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b7aceb2a-7e3e-4d56-86b5-73030df716c4%5C%22%3EIt%20took%20my%20son%20less%20than%208%20hours%20total%20to%20build%20a%20video%20game%20with%20Copilot%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprice-gaming-inflation-xbox-playstation-nintendo-switch-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egaming%20platform%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20Steam%20where%20my%20son%20sometimes%20browses%20to%20play%20free%20game%20demos.%20He%20doesn't%20have%20a%20paid%20account%20on%20the%20site%2C%20but%20he%20explores%20the%20games%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20school%2C%20he%20had%20read%20a%20book%20called%20%26quot%3BMrs.%20Frisby%20and%20the%20Rats%20of%20NIMH%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20something%20about%20this%20book%20caught%20his%20attention.%20It%20reminded%20him%20of%20a%20civilization-building%20game%20he%20had%20seen%20on%20Steam%20that%20he%20thought%20was%20really%20cool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20me%20he%20just%20started%20asking%20Copilot%20questions%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BHelp%20me%20build%20this%20game.%20Here's%20my%20idea.%20How%20could%20I%20build%20this%20game%3F%26quot%3B%20Then%20the%20model%20started%20walking%20him%20through%20the%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20asked%20him%20how%20long%20it%20took%20to%20build%2C%20he%20said%20it%20was%20four%20days%20of%20working%20with%20Copilot%20for%20an%20hour%20or%20two%20a%20day%20until%20he%20got%20a%20workable%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22db836140-3e74-433b-8e04-8ce394729132%5C%22%3EHe%20said%20AI%20never%20gets%20mad%20at%20him%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20best%20parts%20of%20working%20with%20AI%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusiness-owners-explain-how-to-train-ai-employees-better-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20never%20gets%20frustrated%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20he%20asks%20a%20question%20over%20again%3B%20it%20just%20repeats%20the%20answer%20in%20a%20different%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-guide-prompt-engineering-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHis%20favorite%20prompt%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20asking%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20does%20this%20mean%3F%26quot%3B%20If%20he%20gets%20an%20error%20code%20he%20doesn't%20understand%2C%20he'll%20copy%20it%20back%20into%20Copilot%2C%20and%20it%20will%20walk%20him%20through%20it.%20If%20it's%20still%20too%20technical%2C%20he'll%20ask%20the%20question%20again%2C%20and%20it%20will%20simplify%20the%20response%20even%20further.%20He%20also%20uses%20voice%20mode%20to%20talk%20to%20the%20model%20when%20he%20finds%20it%20hard%20to%20type%20out%20what%20he%20wants%20to%20ask.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20hardest%20part%20is%20that%20he%20can%20get%20stuck%20with%20the%20same%20error%2C%20and%20neither%20he%20nor%20the%20AI%20can%20fix%20it%20or%20diagnose%20the%20problem.%20He%20doesn't%20have%20the%20maturity%20yet%20to%20understand%20that%20when%20that%20happens%2C%20he%20has%20to%20do%20something%20different%2C%20or%20prompt%20it%20in%20a%20different%20way%2C%20or%20he's%20going%20to%20keep%20getting%20the%20same%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20somethings%20not%20working%2C%20if%20he%20can%2C%20he'll%20move%20on%20or%20try%20to%20work%20around%20it.%20For%20example%2C%20he%20changed%20the%20rats%20to%20smiley%20faces%20because%20the%20game%20kept%20crashing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225e5eaef2-f5d9-4c28-9664-daf254666fb5%5C%22%3EI%20have%20worries%20about%20his%20AI%20use%2C%20but%20the%20creative%20benefits%20are%20huge%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20it%20was%20a%20low-risk%20environment%20in%20the%20specific%20game%20that%20he%20was%20building.%20I%20wasn't%20concerned%20that%20inappropriate%20content%20or%20responses%20would%20come%20up.%20Still%2C%20I%20wonder%20whether%20he%20has%20the%20ability%20to%20spot%20if%20something%20is%20incorrect%2C%20or%20if%20AI%20has%20given%20him%20information%20that%20is%20not%20right%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20think%20about%20the%20games%20he's%20seeing%20online%20on%20this%20gaming%20platform%20that%20anyone%20can%20post%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20like%20to%20let%20our%20kids%20explore%20on%20their%20own%20and%20then%20show%20us%20what%20they're%20learning%2C%20but%20as%20a%20parent%2C%20have%20I%20put%20the%20proper%20parental%20controls%20on%20what%20my%20son's%20seeing%20and%20what%20he's%20able%20to%20build%20online%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20building%20a%20game%20was%20entirely%20my%20son's%20idea%2C%20executed%20with%20the%20help%20of%20AI%2C%20and%20he%20had%20no%20other%20way%20to%20do%20it%20because%20he%20doesn't%20know%20how%20to%20code.%20I%20think%2C%20for%20him%2C%20using%20AI%20almost%20amplified%20his%20creative%20juices%20because%20there's%20a%20positive%20reward%20in%20actually%20making%20something%20he%20can%20use%20and%20play%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225e4a189f-0f4d-44c1-8828-6406fc659da1%5C%22%3EI%20think%20schools%20should%20teach%20kids%20how%20to%20use%20AI%20appropriately%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20schools%20that%20aren't%20teaching%20students%20how%20to%20use%20AI%20are%20doing%20a%20huge%20disservice.%20I%20work%20for%20a%20tech%20company%2C%20but%20I%20have%20conversations%20with%20friends%20who%20don't%20work%20in%20tech%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-normies-embrace-ai-solve-daily-problems-save-money-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethey%20are%20using%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20so%20many%20ways%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20friend%20who%20was%20job-hunting%20told%20me%20she%20had%20Claude%20help%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-interview-ai-recruitment-tool-consulting-quantitative-case-study-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epractice%20for%20interviews%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20she%20used%20it%20daily%20in%20her%20job%20search.%20Even%20when%20Googling%20something%2C%20you%20get%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-new-ai-search-will-ruin-internet-web-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ean%20AI-generated%20response%3C%2Fa%3E%20right%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20coming%20so%20fast%20and%20furious%2C%20and%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20disservice%20that%20we're%20not%20teaching%20kids%20how%20to%20use%20it%20in%20an%20appropriate%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20my%20son%20if%20there%20was%20anything%20else%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20build%2C%20or%20anything%20else%20he's%20excited%20about%20with%20AI.%20His%20face%20lit%20up%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20next%20game%20idea%20that%20he%20has.%20As%20a%20parent%2C%20it's%20amazing%20to%20see%20your%20kid%20get%20that%20positive%20reinforcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20AI%20and%20parenting%3F%20If%20so%2C%20please%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20reporter%20at%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aaapplegate%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eaapplegate%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F11-year-old-built-his-own-video-game-with-ai-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783249561000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a43f99ea25092c74cca18af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F11-year-old-built-his-own-video-game-with-ai-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%2011-year-old%20used%20AI%20to%20build%20his%20own%20video%20game.%20His%20mother%20supports%20AI%20learning%20for%20kids%20at%20home%20and%20school.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aapplegate%40insider.com%20(Agnes%20Applegate)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22t