0%26quot%3Bthe%20lazy%20way%26quot%3B%20to%20invest.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20also%20invests%20in%20real%20estate%2C%20shifting%20from%20rentals%20to%20syndications.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECody%20Berman%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-financial-independence-fire-movement-investing-saving-early-retirement-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eachieved%20financial%20independence%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20following%20a%20simple%20rule%3A%20Keep%20your%20expenses%20below%20your%20income%20and%20invest%20the%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20various%20side%20hustles%20and%20entrepreneurial%20ventures%2C%20he%20widened%20the%20gap%20between%20what%20he%20earned%20and%20what%20he%20spent%20throughout%20his%20early%2020s.%20By%202021%2C%20shortly%20before%20his%2026th%20birthday%2C%20Berman%20said%20he%20had%20about%20%24500%2C000%20invested%20in%20the%20stock%20market%2C%2013%20rental%20units%20producing%20about%20%243%2C700%20a%20month%20in%20cash%20flow%2C%20and%20a%20digital-products%20business%20earning%20more%20than%20%2410%2C000%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20the%20point%20when%20he%20considered%20himself%20financially%20independent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reviewed%20screenshots%20of%20Berman's%20Vanguard%2C%20Schwab%2C%20and%20Empower%20accounts%20showing%20that%20his%20net%20worth%20exceeded%20%241%20million%20as%20of%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229e84f40c-2acc-413f-bf37-786fce995fc3%5C%22%3EUsing%20the%20%26quot%3Blazy%20way%26quot%3B%20to%20build%20a%20seven-figure%20net%20worth%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20proponents%20of%20the%20FIRE%20movement%2C%20Berman%20invests%20much%20of%20his%20money%20in%20low-cost%20index%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20lazy%20way%20to%20invest%20in%20a%20good%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fretireby30book.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERetire%20by%2030%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BYou%20just%20set%20it%20and%20forget%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndex-fund%20investors%20don't%20have%20to%20pick%20individual%20companies%20or%20try%20to%20predict%20which%20businesses%20will%20outperform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20not%20playing%20a%20guessing%20game.%20You're%20not%20playing%20the%20lottery%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Berman.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20just%20investing%20in%20the%20economy%20as%20a%20whole.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20an%20effective%20strategy%2C%20he%20added%2C%20pointing%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-wins-million-dollar-bet-against-hedge-funds-2018-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWarren%20Buffett's%20famous%20bet%20against%20a%20group%20of%20hedge%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20which%20the%20billionaire%20investor%20wagered%20that%20an%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20index%20fund%20would%20outperform%20a%20collection%20of%20actively%20managed%20funds%20over%20a%2010-year%20period%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20just%20me%20saying%2C%20'Pick%20the%20index%20because%20it's%20easy.'%20It%20actually%20works%2C%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22cody%20berman%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a468a6965e65d39ff1c8fe2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222432%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBerman%20said%20he%20uses%20index%20funds%20to%20%26quot%3Bbuild%20wealth%20on%20autopilot.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Cody%20Berman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBerman%20also%20referenced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fforgetful-investors-performed-best-2014-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20widely%20circulated%20Fidelity%20anecdote%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggesting%20that%20some%20of%20the%20best-performing%20investors%20were%20those%20who%20forgot%20about%20their%20accounts%20%E2%80%94%20a%20reminder%20that%20frequent%20tinkering%20can%20hurt%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20just%20set%20it%20and%20forget%20it%20and%20leave%20it%20in%20a%20low-cost%20index%20fund%2C%20that's%20probably%20going%20to%20be%20the%20right%20answer%20for%2099.9%25%20of%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20stuff%20isn't%20rocket%20science.%20Once%20you%20know%20what%20index%20funds%20to%20buy%2C%20you%20can%20kind%20of%20set%20up%20a%20system%20on%20autopilot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20approach%20appealed%20to%20him%20because%20it%20eliminated%20the%20need%20for%20in-the-moment%20discipline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20such%20a%20systems%20guy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Berman%2C%20who%20automatically%20moves%20a%20set%20amount%20of%20money%20from%20his%20bank%20account%20into%20a%20specific%20index%20fund%20each%20month.%20%26quot%3BSystems%20beat%20willpower%20every%20single%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBerman%20said%20he%20didn't%20spend%20much%20time%20contributing%20to%20a%20corporate%20retirement%20plan%20because%20his%20stint%20in%20a%20traditional%20job%20was%20brief.%20Since%20becoming%20an%20entrepreneur%2C%20however%2C%20he%20has%20prioritized%20tax-advantaged%20accounts.%20He%20said%20he%20maxes%20out%20an%20IRA%2C%20a%20solo%20401(k)%2C%20and%20an%20HSA%20each%20year%2C%20while%20any%20money%20left%20over%20goes%20into%20a%20taxable%20brokerage%20account%20or%20real%20estate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e7a00a78-8670-4439-986d-779476eb4921%5C%22%3EReal%20estate%20investing%3A%20From%20rentals%20to%20syndications%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20starting%20with%20a%20house%20hack%20to%20eliminate%20their%20housing%20expense%2C%20Berman%20and%20his%20wife%20bought%2011%20rental%20units%20between%20late%202020%20and%20mid-2021.%20They%20put%20roughly%20%24200%2C000%20toward%20down%20payments%2C%20he%20said%2C%20and%20the%20properties%20generated%20enough%20cash%20flow%20to%20cover%20much%20of%20their%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20liked%20that%20rentals%20provided%20recurring%20monthly%20income.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20it's%20not%20like%20I'm%20selling%20off%20investments%20every%20month%20to%20live.%20But%20with%20real%20estate%2C%20we're%20actually%20getting%20rent%20in%20our%20account.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20he%20has%20been%20shifting%20away%20from%20rentals%2C%20which%20can%20be%20time-consuming%20due%20to%20maintenance%20and%20tenant%20management%2C%20and%20toward%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investing-ideas-passive-income-strategies-syndications-private-lending-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20more%20passive%20real-estate%20strategy%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20syndications%2C%20which%20allow%20investors%20to%20participate%20in%20larger%20real-estate%20deals%20without%20personally%20buying%20or%20operating%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20still%20want%20the%20real-estate%20exposure%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20go%20out%20there%20and%20just%20buy%20a%2020-unit%20apartment%20building%20myself%20and%20then%20have%20to%20get%20it%20tenanted%20and%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20set%20up%20all%20the%20maintenance%20stuff%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20described%20the%20syndication%20strategy%20as%20%26quot%3Bowning%20rental%20properties%20without%20actually%20having%20to%20own%20rental%20properties.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20it's%20index%20funds%20or%20real-estate%20syndications%2C%20Berman%20is%20looking%20for%20the%20same%20thing%3A%20investments%20that%20can%20compound%20in%20the%20background%20while%20he%20focuses%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-independence-investing-index-funds-millennial-fire-real-estate-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783243801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4677a41aaffe3020cb2a6f%3Fformat%3D