0stood%20out%20for%20their%20food%2C%20comfort%2C%20and%20entertainment.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EChina%20Eastern's%20staff%20was%20nice%2C%20but%20the%20app%20was%20hard%20to%20navigate%2C%20and%20the%20amenities%20were%20lacking.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20flown%20on%20a%20dozen%20major%20airlines%20in%20my%20trial-and-error%20quest%20to%20find%20the%20least%20painful%20options%20for%20my%20frequent%20transoceanic%20trips%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20four%20years%20of%20exclusively%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-vs-delta-united-airlines-economy-compared-flight-review-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflying%20economy%20class%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20comparing%20seats%2C%20service%2C%20entertainment%2C%20food%2C%20and%20prices%2C%20I've%20found%20Etihad%20Airways%2C%20Air%20France%2C%20and%20American%20Airlines%20offer%20the%20best%20value%20on%20long-haul%20treks%20%E2%80%94%20while%20China%20Eastern%20Airlines%20wasn't%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20choosing%20flights%2C%20I%20primarily%20look%20for%20the%20cheapest%20seats%20with%20the%20best%20connections%20and%20travel%20times.%20I%20also%20consider%20factors%20like%20how%20easily%20I%20can%20preorder%20a%20vegetarian%20meal%20or%20how%20much%20legroom%20I'll%20have%20at%205-foot-10%2C%20especially%20on%20red-eyes%20when%20I%20want%20to%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20expect%20premium-cabin%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-survive-long-haul-flights-in-economy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eperks%20in%20economy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20particularly%20as%20airlines%20increasingly%20move%20away%20from%20coach%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20front%20of%20the%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20my%20top%20three%20long-haul%20airlines%20offer%20reasonable%20fares%20and%20are%20noticeably%20more%20comfortable%20than%20others%20in%20my%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEtihad%20is%20my%20top%20choice.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225971%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20economy%20cabin%20of%20Etihad's%20Boeing%20787.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a42add9a25092c74cca0f84%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223986%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20economy%20cabin%20of%20Etihad's%20Boeing%20787-9.%20The%20cupholder%20was%20convenient.%3Cp%3Esharrocks%2FGetty%20Images%2FiStockphoto%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20flew%20round-trip%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-etihad-economy-luxurious-worth-it-long-flight-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEtihad%20from%3C%2Fa%3E%20Rome%20to%20Kuala%20Lumpur%20via%20Abu%20Dhabi%20in%20December%20for%20about%20%24600%2C%20and%20it's%20now%20my%20go-to%20airline%20%E2%80%94%20everything%20on%20the%20UAE-based%20carrier%20just%20feels%20a%20bit%20fancier%20than%20any%20other%20major%20airline%20I've%20flown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20aisle%20seat%20on%20the%20Boeing%20787%20was%20well%20cushioned%2C%20and%20the%20wide%20winged%20headrest%2C%20soft%20blanket%2C%20and%20large%20plush%20pillow%20made%20rest%20and%20sleep%20significantly%20easier%20across%20the%20four%20seven-hour%20legs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20seat%20also%20had%20a%20touchscreen%20remote%20and%20extra%20seatback%20pockets%2C%20while%20my%20partner%20bought%20WiFi%20for%20%249.99%20per%20flight%20and%20found%20it%20good%20enough%20to%20work.%20I%20also%20appreciated%20the%20extensive%20selection%20of%20movies%2C%20with%20hundreds%20of%20recent%20films%20in%20multiple%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20the%20flight%20was%20over%20six%20hours%2C%20I%20was%20given%20a%20reusable%20tote%20with%20lotion%2C%20lip%20balm%2C%20an%20eye%20mask%2C%20earplugs%2C%20and%20a%20dental%20kit%20%E2%80%94%20the%20first%20time%20I've%20seen%20that%20kind%20of%20extra%20in%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20food%20was%20also%20a%20highlight.%20I%20easily%20preordered%20a%20vegetarian%20meal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsee-inside-brand-new-etihad-boeing-787-10-dreamliner-greenliner-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20Etihad's%3C%2Fa%3E%20website%2C%20and%20the%20menu%20was%20much%20larger%20than%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20chose%20an%20Indian%20curry%20with%20several%20sides%20that%20was%20better%20than%20some%20restaurant%20meals.%20This%20was%20a%20big%20plus%20since%20good%20airline%20vegetarian%20options%20are%20hard%20to%20find%20or%20preorder%20in%20my%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20liked%20the%20small%20details%20on%20Air%20France.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Airplane%20tray%20table%20with%20a%20packaged%20meal%2C%20bread%2C%20snacks%2C%20water%20bottle%2C%20and%20drink%20cup%20in%20a%20passenger%20seat.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a42d494360acd489560d2bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EExample%20of%20a%20non-vegetarian%20long-haul%20economy%20meal%20on%20Air%20France%20(not%20the%20author's%20exact%20flight).%20It%20includes%20starter%20bread%2C%20a%20choice%20of%20two%20hot%20dishes%2C%20cheese%2C%20and%20a%20dessert.%3Cp%3EMatchaBeer%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20flew%20on%20Air%20France%20from%20Porto%2C%20Portugal%2C%20to%20Bogot%C3%A1%2C%20Colombia%2C%20via%20Paris%20in%202022%2C%20also%20on%20a%20Boeing%20787.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20surprised%20to%20find%20the%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdifference-between-amenities-in-business-and-economy-class-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eupscale%20carrier%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20which%20was%20named%20the%20best%20in%20Western%20Europe%20by%20the%20airline%20ranking%20website%20Skytrax%20in%202025%20%E2%80%94%20offering%20competitive%20prices.%20I%20paid%20about%20%24550.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverything%20seemed%20new%20and%20clean%20from%20my%20aisle%20seat%2C%20and%20the%20plane%20had%20nice%20touches%20like%20a%20coat%20hook%20and%20a%20cup%20holder%20on%20the%20seatback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20particularly%20impressed%20by%20the%20larger%20portion%20sizes%20on%20the%20long-haul%20leg%2C%20and%20the%20French%20pastries%20were%20flaky%20and%20buttery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarted-freelancing-penny-a-word-never-gave-up-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efreelance%20writer%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20often%20works%20on%20the%20go%2C%20the%20free%20WiFi%20and%20seat%20space%20in%20economy%20were%20so%20good%20that%20I%20worked%20most%20of%20the%2010-hour%20flight.%20Air%20France%20consistently%20makes%20long%20travel%20days%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20route%20now%20exclusively%20uses%20the%20Airbus%20A350%2C%20offering%20about%20an%20inch%20more%20shoulder%20room%20and%20faster%20Starlink%20WiFi%20than%20the%20older%20satellite%20system%20on%20my%20flight%20four%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAmerican%20offers%20good%20value%20on%20long-haul%20flights.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22American%20Airlines'%20777-200.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a42c045a25092c74cca1067%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmerican's%20777-200%20is%20among%20its%20older%20planes%2C%20but%20I%20still%20like%20the%20economy%20experience.%3Cp%3ELAX%20via%20Getty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20flew%20American%20from%20Tampa%20to%20Seoul%20via%20Dallas-Fort%20Worth%20in%20February%202025%2C%20and%20it's%20now%20my%20preferred%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbasic-economy-delta-vs-american-airlines-review-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS-based%20airline%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20value%20on%20long-haul%20flights.%20I%20paid%20about%20%24630%3B%20the%20leg%20to%20Seoul%20lasted%20nearly%2015%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20gate%20to%20gate%2C%20I%20found%20the%20experience%20easy%20and%20comfortable.%20Boarding%20the%20Boeing%20777%20was%20smooth%2C%20and%20the%20food%20was%20a%20step%20above%20most%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflown-american-airlines-for-15-years-switching-lufthansa-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elong-haul%20flights%3C%2Fa%3E%20I've%20been%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vegetarian%20meal%2C%20which%20had%20chickpeas%2C%20veggies%2C%20and%20rice%20and%20came%20with%20bread%20and%20dessert%2C%20tasted%20fresh%20and%20was%20easy%20to%20preorder.%20American%20also%20serves%20bibimbap%2C%20a%20South%20Korean%20beef%20dish%2C%20as%20a%20main%20meal%20option%20on%20the%20Seoul%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20coach%20seat%2C%20I%20found%20it%20well-cushioned%2C%20and%20I%20had%20plenty%20of%20legroom%20and%20arm%20space%20in%20my%20middle%20seat%2C%20despite%20the%2010-abreast%20seating%20layout%2C%20which%20is%20standard%20for%20this%20plane%20type.%20It's%20one%20of%20the%20few%20airlines%20on%20which%20I've%20actually%20slept%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmerican%20is%20actively%20upgrading%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflying-american-airlines-to-europe-new-york-madrid-flight-review-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elong-haul%20777%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20787%20fleets%20with%20enhancements%20like%20faster%20WiFi%2C%20Bluetooth%20audio%2C%20and%20more%20charging%20options%20for%20coach%20travelers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EChina%20Eastern%20wasn't%20a%20fit%20for%20me.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20airline's%20logo%20on%20its%20seatback%20television.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a42bee7e218c3b62535ee27%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20photo%20is%20from%20a%20China%20Eastern%20A330%2C%20but%20the%20limited%20English-language%20movie%20selection%20is%20a%20fleet-wide%20characteristic.%3Cp%3Eskyxvolt%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20flew%20China%20Eastern%20for%2013%20hours%20from%20Osaka%2C%20Japan%2C%20to%20Rome%20via%20Shanghai%20in%20June%20last%20year.%20The%20flight%20cost%20about%20%24500%2C%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20cheaper%20than%20most%20of%20the%20comparable%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20morning%20flight%2C%20which%20was%20on%20an%20Airbus%20A350%2C%20landed%20right%20on%20time%2C%20and%20I%20found%20the%20cabin%20crew%20very%20kind.%20My%20middle%20seat%20was%20fine%3B%20it%20came%20with%20linens%20and%20a%20headrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20was%20disappointed%20with%20the%20overall%20flight%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-airline-selling-tickets-for-worlds-longest-direct-flight-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina%20Eastern%3C%2Fa%3E%20website%20and%20mobile%20app%20appeared%20to%20be%20designed%20primarily%20for%20Mandarin-speaking%20users%2C%20and%20checking%20in%20online%20took%20over%20an%20hour%20%E2%80%94%20the%20site%20kept%20switching%20between%20languages%20and%20had%20many%20broken%20links.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20found%20the%20WiFi%20confusing.%20Basic%20speeds%20cost%20%2420%2C%20which%20was%20too%20pricey%20for%20me.%20There's%20a%20way%20to%20get%20free%20internet%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20clear%20at%20the%20time%20of%20booking%20and%20requires%20passengers%20to%20pre-register%20for%20a%20limited%20pool%20of%20first-come%2C%20first-served%20passes%20before%20the%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20didn't%20like%20the%20food%20or%20the%20entertainment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20broccoli-and-rice%20dish%20was%20overly%20sweet%20for%20my%20taste%2C%20and%20the%20veggies%20in%20my%20noodle%20dish%20tasted%20overcooked.%20It%20was%20all%20very%20one-note%20and%20among%20my%20least%20favorite%20airplane%20meals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20I%20thought%20the%20movie%20options%20were%20lacking%2C%20consisting%20almost%20exclusively%20of%20Chinese%20films%20and%20offering%20limited%20subtitle%20options.%20I%20recognize%20the%20airline%20probably%20serves%20Chinese%20customers%20better%2C%20but%20as%20an%20American%2C%20it%20wasn't%20enjoyable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20a%20reminder%20to%20always%20bring%20my%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsolo-travel-tips-for-long-haul-trips%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esnacks%20and%20movies%3C%2Fa%3E%20rather%20than%20relying%20on%20the%20airline's%20offerings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20Eastern%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider%20for%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflown-dozen-airlines-3-recommend-one-avoid-etihad-american-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783242001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a42cec1e218c3b62535ef11%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflown-dozen-airlines-3-recommend-one-avoid-etihad-american-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I've%20tested%20a%20dozen%20different%20airlines%20to%20find%20the%20best%20for%20long-haul%20travel.%20Etihad%20Airways%20exceeded%20expectations%2C%20while%20China%20Eastern%20wasn't%20for%20me.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Catherine%20Work)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Saving%20Rs%2030%2C000%20a%20month'%3A%20Corporate%20couple%20reveals%20how%20moving%20to%20Manali%20changed%20everything%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783242000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132192468%2Cimgsize-159471.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F