s-coney-island%2Famp_articleshow%2F132193055.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Henry%20Blodget%20says%20AI%20may%20write%20great%20novels%20someday.%20He%20still%20wanted%20to%20write%20this%20one%20himself.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226888%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Business%20Insider%20founder%20Henry%20Blodget%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4563671aaffe3020cb1743%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224592%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHenry%20Blodget%20spoke%20to%20Business%20Insider%20about%20his%20new%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Upgrade.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ERoy%20Rochlin%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHenry%20Blodget%20told%20Business%20Insider%20why%20he%20wrote%20a%20novel%20about%20an%20AI%20supervillain.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20risks%20are%20big%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20AI%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%2C%20in%20fiction%2C%20gives%20you%20a%20nice%20canvas%20to%20work%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBlodget%20said%20he%20edited%20the%20book%20with%20Claude%2C%20but%20intentionally%20did%20not%20let%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-ai-chatgpt-wont-replace-writers-authors-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20draft%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EVictor%20Leetum%20is%20a%20tech%20billionaire%20with%20a%20plan%3A%20%26quot%3BCloning%20himself%20with%20AI%20so%20he%20can%20live%20forever%20and%20take%20over%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe'll%20do%20anything%20to%20achieve%20his%20goal%2C%20from%20exploiting%20cops%20to%20hiring%20mercenaries%20and%20downing%20planes.%20That%20is%2C%20if%20we're%20to%20believe%20William%20Swain%2C%20the%20narrator%20of%20Business%20Insider%20founder%20Henry%20Blodget's%20new%20page-turner%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Upgrade.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20might%20sound%20familiar.%20Executives%20are%20creating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbny-executive-uses-ai-digital-twin-as-coach-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20twins%20of%20themselves%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They're%20seeking%20the%20fountain%20of%20youth%20via%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-biohacking-wellness-event-best-hacks-not-what-expected-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeptides%2C%20plasma%20infusions%2C%20and%20biohacking%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There's%20also%20a%20swirling%20doomerism%20around%20AI%2C%20one%20that%20shrouds%20its%20leaders%20in%20conspiracy%20theories.%20Don't%20ask%20your%20tinfoil-hat-uncle%20about%20Peter%20Thiel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlodget%20made%20his%20name%20during%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhenry-blodget-ai-bubble-boom-dotcom-interview-peter-kafka-2025-09%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20dot-com%20era%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20when%20stocks%20soared%20and%20wallets%20fattened%20on%20the%20internet's%20growth.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20incredibly%20similar%2C%20except%20it%20basically%20has%20another%20three%20zeroes%20at%20the%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20Blodget%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BThe%20numbers%20are%20astounding.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20book%20is%20a%20way%20of%20reckoning%20with%20all%20that%20money%20and%20pessimism.%20While%20CEOs%20get%20rich%2C%20they%20also%20extol%20the%20risks%20that%20AI%20could%20pose%3A%20the%20wipeout%20of%20the%20workforce%2C%20the%20elimination%20of%20truth%2C%20the%20destruction%20of%20humanity.%20Those%20early%20equity%20holders%20are%20also%20the%20ones%20warning%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-permanent-underclass-500k-san-francisco-debate-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20%26quot%3Bpermanent%20underclass.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20risks%20are%20big%2C%26quot%3B%20Blodget%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%2C%20in%20fiction%2C%20gives%20you%20a%20nice%20canvas%20to%20work%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227950a0a8-a4c4-4538-95c7-5a5e37cc78c9%5C%22%3EBlodget%20says%20he%20wanted%20to%20write%20the%20book%20himself%20%E2%80%94%20but%20allowed%20Claude%20to%20give%20feedback%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Upgrade%26quot%3B%20follows%20Swain%2C%20a%20millionaire%20ex-CEO%20who%20grew%20up%20with%20and%20later%20competed%20against%20the%20more%20deep-pocketed%20Leetum.%20He%20knows%20Leetum's%20sinister%20intentions%3A%20to%20make%20AI%20superbeings%2C%20himself%20chief%20among%20them%2C%20and%20rule%20humanity.%20Swain%20must%20stop%20Leetum's%20plan%20and%20convince%20the%20cops%20he's%20not%20the%20true%20villain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlodget%20is%20an%20analyst%20and%20journalist%20at%20heart%2C%20spending%20years%20on%20Wall%20Street%20before%20founding%20this%20publication.%20Blodget%20stepped%20down%20as%20CEO%20of%20Business%20Insider%20in%202023%2C%20and%20left%20its%20board%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20once%20pursued%20an%20MA%20in%20fiction%20at%20New%20York%20University%2C%20he%20said%2C%20and%20published%20a%20short%20story%2020%20years%20ago.%20This%20moment%2C%20Blodget%20thought%2C%20calls%20for%20the%20form.%20There's%20a%20%26quot%3Bdepth%20of%20life%26quot%3B%20that's%20difficult%20to%20access%20in%20tech%20non-fiction%2C%20Blodget%20said%2C%20and%20life%20is%20exactly%20what%20writing%20needs%20in%20the%20AI%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20in%20his%20writing%20process%2C%20Blodget%20said%20a%20friend%20called%20him%20an%20%26quot%3Bidiot%26quot%3B%20for%20not%20writing%20the%20novel%20with%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20no%20doubt%20that%20Claude%2C%20ChatGPT%2C%20and%20others%20are%20going%20to%20write%20really%20good%20books%20at%20some%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20I%20actually%20wanted%20to%20write%20it.%20The%20point%20was%20to%20do%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20still%20used%20AI%20in%20the%20editing%20process.%20He%20shortened%20an%20early%20hospital%20scene%20after%20Claude%20said%20it%20was%20getting%20boring.%20He%20also%20asked%20Claude%20to%20%26quot%3Bfact-check%26quot%3B%20the%20book%2C%20ensuring%20that%20he%20didn't%20contradict%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20Claude's%20feedback%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-ai-may-be-making-us-worse-at-handling-conflict-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewas%20%26quot%3Bsuckup-y%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20misremembered%20plot%20points%2C%20he%20said.%20Still%2C%20Blodget%20has%20no%20shame%20in%20his%20AI%20use%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0even%20while%20writing%20about%20how%20AI%20could%20ruin%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20takes%20a%20human%20seven%20hours%20to%20read%20a%20book%2C%26quot%3B%20Blodget%20said.%20%26quot%3BTo%20have%20it%20done%20in%2017%20seconds%20is%20astonishing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20book's%20cover%20is%20emblazoned%20with%20a%20review%20from%20Claude%3A%20%26quot%3BUnforgettable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22838%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20cover%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Upgrade%26quot%3B%20by%20Henry%20Blodget%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4680001bba93485607a9dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221256%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOn%20the%20cover%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Upgrade%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20AI%20chatbot%20Claude%20calls%20Henry%20Blodget's%20book%20%26quot%3Bunforgettable.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EHenry%20Blodget%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224ffabd9b-da8e-4848-b2c5-8ee11be97e1f%5C%22%3EAI%20twins%20and%20data%20centers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20things%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Upgrade%26quot%3B%20are%20purely%20fictionalized.%20Blodget%20added%20a%20new%20element%20to%20the%20periodic%20table%2C%20after%20all.%20Others%20are%20painstakingly%20realistic%2C%20he%20said%2C%20like%20long%20descriptions%20of%20data%20centers%20or%20definitions%20of%20consciousness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20the%20in-between%20%E2%80%94%20realistic%2C%20but%20not%20yet%20feasible.%20Swain%20lost%20his%20daughter%2C%20Loon%2C%20before%20the%20book's%20start.%20When%20Leetum%20produces%20a%20hyperrealistic%20AI%20version%20of%20her%2C%20Swain%20spends%20much%20of%20the%20novel%20trying%20to%20save%20his%20digital%20daughter%20from%20a%20second%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20already%20have%20pretty%20sophisticated%20AI%20twins%2C%26quot%3B%20Blodget%20said.%20%26quot%3BNo%20one%20is%20thinking%2C%20'Hey%2C%20it's%20a%20conscious%20entity%2C'%20but%20that's%20not%20a%20far%20leap.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20us%20are%20living%20in%20this%20in-between%20world.%20Tech%20leaders%20make%20big%20promises%20about%20a%20coming%20AI%20onslaught%2C%20telling%20us%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20world%20we%20haven't%20yet%20seen.%20It's%20helped%20cement%20AI's%20status%20as%20deeply%20unpopular.%20Graduates%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-graduates-ai-backlash-commencement-speeches-anxiety-job-market-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebooing%20references%20to%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20their%20commencement%20ceremonies%2C%20and%20Americans%20would%20rather%20live%20near%20a%20nuclear%20reactor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgallup-opposition-data-centers-nuclear-reactors-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethan%20a%20data%20center%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20visceral%20wave%20of%20animosity%20toward%20AI%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Blodget%20said.%20He%20finds%20the%20job%20apocalypse%20claims%20to%20be%20unfounded%2C%20but%20said%20that%20the%20general%20pessimism%20was%20%26quot%3Btotally%20understandable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20should%20we%20read%20a%20novel%20about%20AI%20supervillains%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI%20hate%3F%20It's%20not%20a%20doomer%20novel%2C%20Blodget%20said.%20He%20pointed%20to%20the%20novel's%20happy%20ending%20and%20the%20unexpected%20connection%20with%20Swain's%20AI%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20also%20is%20a%20very%20optimistic%20piece%20of%20AI%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20a%20reason%20Blodget%20released%20%26quot%3BThe%20Upgrade%26quot%3B%20first%2C%20rather%20than%20its%20prequel%2C%20a%20space-race%20novel%20about%20Swain's%20origins%20that's%20sitting%20on%20the%20shelf.%20This%20one%20speaks%20to%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20both%20this%20tremendously%2C%20potentially%20scary%20and%20dangerous%20thing%2C%20and%20something%20that%20can%20be%20miraculous%2C%26quot%3B%20Blodget%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20really%20know%20yet%20where%20we%20end%20up%20on%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhenry-blodget-book-the-upgrade-ai-thriller-tech-supervillain-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783241401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4563782680585ce91a335b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhenry-blodget-book-the-upgrade-ai-thriller-tech-supervillain-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Henry%20Blodget%20told%20Business%20Insider%20why%20he%20chose%20to%20edit%20his%20book%20with%20Claude%20%E2%80%94%20but%20wrote%20it%20by%20hand.%20He%20also%20included%20Claude's%20review%20on%20its%20cover.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hchandonnet%40insider.com%20(Henry%20Chandonnet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Egg%20companies%20made%20%241.22%20billion%20as%20Americans%20paid%20over%20%246%20a%20dozen%3B%20now%20they'll%20donate%2053%20million%20eggs%20in%20DOJ%20settlement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783241205000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%