rd%20Sanctuary%2C%20located%20about%2013%20km%20from%20Panvel.%20A%20rickshaw%20costs%20around%20Rs%20250%20one%20way%2C%20while%20a%20bus%20or%20shared%20rickshaw%20will%20cost%20under%20Rs%2030%20per%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEntry%20to%20the%20sanctuary%20is%20Rs%2060%20for%20adults%20and%20Rs%2030%20for%20children.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20small%20refundable%20deposit%20for%20plastic%20bottles%2C%20as%20the%20park%20strictly%20enforces%20a%20no-plastic%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpend%20the%20day%20walking%20through%20the%20sanctuary%E2%80%99s%20shaded%20trails.%20Home%20to%20over%20150%20species%20of%20resident%20and%20migratory%20birds%2C%20including%20the%20Malabar%20grey%20hornbill%2C%20golden%20oriole%2C%20and%20paradise%20flycatcher%2C%20it%20is%20a%20place%20for%20nature%20lovers.%20Benches%20are%20placed%20along%20the%20paths%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F413732%2Fkoynanagar-young-guides-are-reviving-tourism-and-creating-jobs-homestays%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eideal%20for%20resting%20and%20birdwatching%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-01T214237.289_11zon-1756743171.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Karnala%20Fort%20trail%20begins%20inside%20the%20sanctuary%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Mumbai%20Pune%20Adventures%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-01T214237.289_11zon-1756743171.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-01T214237.289_11zon-1756743171-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-01T214237.289_11zon-1756743171-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-01T214237.289_11zon-1756743171-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-01T214237.289_11zon-1756743171-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-494890%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Karnala%20Fort%20trail%20begins%20inside%20the%20sanctuary%3B%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mumbaipuneadventures.com%2Fdestination%2Fkarnala-fort-trekking-near-mumbai-pune%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPicture%20source%3A%20Mumbai%20Pune%20Adventures%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBring%20your%20own%20snacks%20and%20water%2C%20as%20food%20stalls%20inside%20the%20park%20are%20limited.%20There%20are%20designated%20picnic%20spots%2C%20making%20it%20a%20great%20setting%20for%20an%20outdoor%20lunch.%20Return%20to%20Panvel%20in%20the%20evening%20and%20enjoy%20a%20local%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDay%203%3A%20Trek%20to%20Karnala%20Fort%20%E2%80%93%20Light%20adventure%20and%20history%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%20is%20ideal%20for%20the%20moderate%20trek%20to%20Karnala%20Fort.%20Start%20early%20to%20avoid%20the%20afternoon%20heat.%20The%20fort%20trail%20begins%20inside%20the%20sanctuary%20and%20covers%20about%20three%20to%20four%20kilometres%20one%20way%2C%20with%20an%20ascent%20of%20one%20and%20a%20half%20to%20two%20hours%20through%20lush%20forest%20and%20rocky%20terrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trek%20is%20suitable%20for%20families%20